Package: AlexBot
Type: Package
Title: ONS Boundary Guessing Game Tools
Version: 0.3.1
Authors@R: c(person(given = "pd-luhc", role = c("aut"), comment = c(GitHub = "https://github.com/pd-luhc")),
             person(given = "M365 Copilot", role = c("cre"), email = "noreply@microsoft.com"))
Description: Helpers to download ONS boundary data (Local Authorities and more),
    pick specific or random entries, plot silhouettes and surroundings for
    a geography guessing game, and generate nearby multiple-choice options.
